I wish to emphasize that I have chosen to plead guilty, fully recognizing the significance of this action as a mitigating factor. By doing so, I intend to demonstrate my sincere acceptance of responsibility and save valuable time and resources for this honorable court. My guilty plea not only speaks to my willingness to make amends but also benefits the court by avoiding the need for a protracted legal process.

